-- Consumer-Behavior Research Firm Envirosell Opens Istanbul Office
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-08-16T10:31:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/consumer-behavior-research-firm-envirosell-opens-istanbul-office.html
Envirosell , the New York-based
consumer behavior research and consulting firm founded by Paco
Underhill, opened an office in Istanbul, it said.  The firm, whose clients include  The Gap (GPS) , Adidas,  BP Plc (BP/)  and
 Wal-Mart Stores Inc. (WMT) , will offer marketing and sales consultancy
to companies in  Turkey , the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
 eersoy@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  